com.facebook.buck.core.build.engine

Class BuildResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.build.engine.BuildResult

  • public abstract class BuildResult
extends Object
    This is a union type that represents either a success or a failure. This exists so that com.facebook.buck.core.build.engine.impl.CachingBuildEngine#buildOnceDepsAreBuilt() can return a strongly typed value.
